---
title: Black Bean & Poblano Quesadillas with Salsa Fresca & Lime Sour Cream
description: As we’ve grown more sophisticated in this life, so have our quesadillas. Gone are the days of those microwaved renditions of our youth (they got the job done, but they definitely weren’t delicious). This version is jam-packed with tender poblano, flavorful mashed black beans, and tons of gooey, melty cheese. On top, there’s a tangy salsa fresca and dollops of lime sour cream. Yep, a good thing just got a whole lot better.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5fb7f249e9825811b22ee81f-328146ec.jpg
